txt.en: Defeat spiders in the Tower of Cirith Ungol ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'Nar, not again! Can you hear them, Silent One?'

You shrug.

'Damned, little spiders skittering about in the tower! I found a few of 'em in the pot earlier, and I'm not going to cook while they're crawling about!

'Find those little biters and get rid of them, will you?'
Defeated spiders in the Tower of Cirith Ungol ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Spiders can be found lurking in the shadows of the Tower of Cirith Ungol.\n\nLúksu has asked you to slay the small spiders that have snuck into the Tower of Cirith Ungol.
You have defeated many of the small spiders that made their way into the Tower of Cirith Ungol.
